Aplicacion de parches - Grid y Oracle (G/O)

1. Verificar la versión de parches existentes (G/O)
	$ORACLE_HOME/OPatch/opatch version


-----Respaldar  el directorio raiz de los productos de oracle.

2. Actualizar OPatch en caso de ser necesario.

	2.1 Realizar el respaldo del Opatch anterior antes de descomprimir el nuevo (G/O)
		$ cd $ORACLE_HOME
		$ ls -ld OP*
		$ mv OPatch OPatch_YB_08072024

		2.2 Descomprimir el OPatch actualizado
	
			2.2.1 Para Grid.	Verificar el owner de la carpeta grid/
				# cd /oracle/app/product/19c
				# ls -ltr
				# chown grid grid/ ----> chown usuario directorio
	
			2.2.2 Desde Grid.
				Ubicar la ruta donde esta ubicado el OPatch 
				$ pwd -> /exportdb/parches
				$ cd $ORACLE_HOME
				$ unzip -q /exportdb/parches/p6880880_190000_Linux-x86-64.zip  ----> /ruta/nombre_OPatch
				
			2.2.3 Para Grid (Devolver el paso del owner)
				# chown root grid/

			2.2.4 Para Oracle.
				Ubicar la ruta donde esta ubicado el OPatch 
				$ pwd -> /exportdb/parches
				$ cd $ORACLE_HOME
				$ unzip -q /exportdb/parches/p6880880_190000_Linux-x86-64.zip

3. Validar PreReq para instalación de parches (G/O)

	3.1 Grid
		$ echo $UNZIPPED_PATCH_LOCATION
		$ export UNZIPPED_PATCH_LOCATION=/exportdb/parches/35742441
		$ $ORACLE_HOME/OPatch/opatch prereq CheckConflictAgainstOHWithDetail -phBaseDir $UNZIPPED_PATCH_LOCATION/35642822/35643107
		$ $ORACLE_HOME/OPatch/opatch prereq CheckConflictAgainstOHWithDetail -phBaseDir $UNZIPPED_PATCH_LOCATION/35642822/35655527
		$ $ORACLE_HOME/OPatch/opatch prereq CheckConflictAgainstOHWithDetail -phBaseDir $UNZIPPED_PATCH_LOCATION/35642822/35652062
		$ $ORACLE_HOME/OPatch/opatch prereq CheckConflictAgainstOHWithDetail -phBaseDir $UNZIPPED_PATCH_LOCATION/35642822/35553096
		$ $ORACLE_HOME/OPatch/opatch prereq CheckConflictAgainstOHWithDetail -phBaseDir $UNZIPPED_PATCH_LOCATION/35642822/33575402

	3.2 Oracle
		$ echo $UNZIPPED_PATCH_LOCATION
		$ export UNZIPPED_PATCH_LOCATION=/exportdb/parches/35742441
		$ $ORACLE_HOME/OPatch/opatch prereq CheckConflictAgainstOHWithDetail -phBaseDir $UNZIPPED_PATCH_LOCATION/35642822/35643107
		$ $ORACLE_HOME/OPatch/opatch prereq CheckConflictAgainstOHWithDetail -phBaseDir $UNZIPPED_PATCH_LOCATION/35642822/35655527

	3.3 Grid
		3.3.1	$ cat <<EOF >> /tmp/patch_list_gihome.txt
		 		$UNZIPPED_PATCH_LOCATION/35642822/35643107
		 		$UNZIPPED_PATCH_LOCATION/35642822/35655527
		 		$UNZIPPED_PATCH_LOCATION/35642822/35652062
		 		$UNZIPPED_PATCH_LOCATION/35642822/35553096
		 		$UNZIPPED_PATCH_LOCATION/35642822/33575402
		 		EOF

		3.3.2   Verificar espacio disponible en el home para aplicar parche.
				$ $ORACLE_HOME/OPatch/opatch prereq CheckSystemSpace -phBaseFile /tmp/patch_list_gihome.txt
		
	3.4 Oracle
		3.4.1   $cat <<EOF >> /tmp/patch_list_dbhome.txt
				$UNZIPPED_PATCH_LOCATION/35642822/35643107
				$UNZIPPED_PATCH_LOCATION/35642822/35655527
				EOF

		3.4.2	Verificar espacio disponible en el home para aplicar parche.
				$ $ORACLE_HOME/OPatch/opatch prereq CheckSystemSpace -phBaseFile /tmp/patch_list_dbhome.txt

4. Instalación del RU

	4.1 Para Grid
		$ORACLE_HOME =
		# export CV_ASSUME_DISTID=OL7 ## Para oracle linux 8
		# export UNZIPPED_PATCH_LOCATION=/exportdb/parches/35742441
		# export PATH=$PATH:ORACLE_HOME/OPatch

		# cd /tmp
		# opatchauto apply $UNZIPPED_PATCH_LOCATION/35642822

	4.2 Para Oracle
		$ORACLE_HOME =
		 //// No hacerlo en la misma ventana que se realizo el de grid***
		# export CV_ASSUME_DISTID=OL7 ## Para oracle linux 8
		# export UNZIPPED_PATCH_LOCATION=/exportdb/parches/35742441
		# export PATH=$PATH:/oracle/app/oracle19/product/19c/db1/OPatch

		# cd /tmp
		# opatchauto apply $UNZIPPED_PATCH_LOCATION/35642822 -oh /oracle/app/oracle19/product/19c/db1


5. Instalacion del OJVM (Database Embedded JVM Java)

	5.1 Oracle
		$ $ORACLE_HOME/OPatch/opatch lspatches
		$ $ORACLE_HOME /oracle/app/oracle19/product/19c/db1


	5.2 Grid
		$ $ORACLE_HOME /oracle/app/product/19c/grid
		$ crsctl stop has
		$ (/oracle/app/product/19c/grid/bin/crsctl stop has)

	5.3 Oracle
		$ ls -ld
		$ export PATCH_TOP_DIR=/exportdb/parches
		$ cd $PATCH_TOP_DIR
		$ mv PatchSearch.xml PatchSearch.xml_35742441
		$ unzip -q p36155925_1921000DBRU_Linux-x86-64.zip
		$ cd $PATCH_TOP_DIR/
		$ $ORACLE_HOME/OPatch/opatch prereq CheckConflictAgainstOHWithDetail -ph ./36155925
		$ $ORACLE_HOME/OPatch/opatch napply ./36155925 -verbose

	5.4 Grid
		$ ls -ld
		$ export PATCH_TOP_DIR=/exportdb/parches
		$ cd $PATCH_TOP_DIR
		$ mv PatchSearch.xml PatchSearch.xml_36155925
		$ unzip -q p36155938_1921000DBRU_Linux-x86-64.zip

	5.5 Root
		$ $ORACLE_HOME /oracle/app/product/19c/grid
		$ export PATCH_TOP_DIR=/exportdb/parches
		$ export PATH=$PATH:/oracle/app/product/19c/grid/OPatch
		$ cd $PATCH_TOP_DIR/
		$ opatchauto apply ./36155938 -analyze
		$ opatchauto apply ./36155938
		$ $ORACLE_HOME/OPatch/opatch lsinventory > $HOME/opatch_lsinventory.txt


